interpretation:
The "woman in tuxedo" emoji represents a confident, stylish, and empowered woman who is unafraid to challenge traditional gender norms. She is a trailblazer who defies societal expectations and embraces her own unique identity. This card encourages you to be true to yourself and not conform to the expectations of others. It reminds you that you have the power to define your own sense of style, personality, and identity.

In a reading, the "woman in tuxedo" card may indicate that you are in a position of power or influence, and that you are not afraid to speak your mind and assert your authority. It can also suggest that you are breaking free from old patterns and expectations, and that you are discovering a new sense of self. This card is a reminder to be proud of who you are, to embrace your unique identity, and to celebrate your own individuality.
